How to purchase MEPENOMICS

K LDownload and Install Metamask wallet

Step 1: Visit https://Metamask.io/download
and select your browser.

Step 2: Follow the steps in your respective extension store to add the Metamask wallet extension to your browser. After installing, you should see the Metamask open in a new tab.

Step 3: Follow the steps at https://learn.metamask.io/lessons/what-is-a-crypto-wallet 

 

K LDeposit Eth

Step 1: Follow the instructions at https://Metamask.app/learn/guides/how-to-deposit-eth-matic-and-sol-in-my-Metamask-wallet to deposit Eth.

K LSwap your ETH for MEPENOMICS

Connect your wallet to app.uniswap.org (the correct contract will show up) and click the swap button!
